{"word":"G4026 - περιΐστημι - periḯstēmi - per-ee-is'-tay-mee - Avoid","slug":"G4026","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">περιΐστημι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>periḯstēmi"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>per-ee-is'-tay-mee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Avoid"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03B5;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x03B9;&#x0344;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03B7;&#x03BC;&#x03B9; - periiste&#x0304;mi</b> - <i>per-ee-is'-tay-mee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4012\">G4012</a> and <a href=\"#/G2476\">G2476</a>; to <i>stand</i> all <i>around</i>, that is, (near) to <i>be a bystander</i>, or (aloof) to <i>keep away</i> from: - avoid, shun, stand by (round about)."}]}